title: Viscera Pots
description: Amalgamation of over 12 pots smashed together in a pile with strands of viscera oozing out from every opening, decorated in red glaze. A human heart is placed in the center with a little white flower growing proudly out of the aorta. New life can grow out of all things, even the most visceral.
